### Phase 6 — Tasks slice smoke tests (UC-8, UC-9, BR-3, BR-5)
### Prereqs: backend on http://localhost:8080 with seeded users (pm/ba/emp)
### and at least one ACTIVE goal. Run requests top-to-bottom.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. PM login
# @name pmLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "pm", "password": "pmPass1!"}

> {% client.global.set("pmToken", response.body.token); %}

### 2. BA login
# @name baLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "ba", "password": "baPass1!"}

> {% client.global.set("baToken", response.body.token); %}

### 3. EMPLOYEE login
# @name empLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "emp", "password": "empPass1!"}

> {% client.global.set("empToken", response.body.token); %}

### 4. PM creates a goal to host the tasks → 201
# @name createGoal
POST {{host}}/api/v1/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Цель под задачи Q1",
  "periodStart": "2026-01-01",
  "periodEnd": "2026-12-31",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "kpis": [{"name": "KPI-1", "targetValue": 100, "currentValue": 0, "unit": "шт."}]
}

> {% client.global.set("goalId", response.body.id); %}

### 5. PM activates the goal (tasks can live on ACTIVE/DRAFT goals; archived is blocked)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/goals/{{goalId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

###
POST {{host}}/api/v1/goals/{{goalId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "ACTIVE"}

### 6. PM creates a task (UC-8) → 201
# @name createTask
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Подготовить проектный каркас",
  "description": "Репозиторий + CI + линтер",
  "goalId": "{{goalId}}",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "deadline": "2026-06-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("taskId", response.body.id); %}

### 7. BA tries to create a task → 403 (PM-only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{baToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"title": "BA задача", "goalId": "{{goalId}}", "priority": "LOW"}

### 8. EMPLOYEE tries to change status of unassigned task → 400 (BR-3)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "IN_PROGRESS"}

### 9. PM tries to move TODO → IN_PROGRESS without assignee → 400 (BR-3)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "IN_PROGRESS"}

### 10. PM assigns the task to the employee → 200
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/assignee
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"assignee": "emp"}

### 11. PM assigns to BA → 400 (BR-5: only EMPLOYEE role can be assigned)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/assignee
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"assignee": "ba"}

### 12. EMPLOYEE moves TODO → IN_PROGRESS → 200
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "IN_PROGRESS"}

### 13. EMPLOYEE moves IN_PROGRESS → DONE → 200
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "DONE"}

### 14. EMPLOYEE tries DONE → IN_PROGRESS → 400 (DONE is terminal)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "IN_PROGRESS"}

### 15. PM lists every task → 200, sees all
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}

### 16. EMPLOYEE lists tasks → 200, UC-9 scoping: only assignedTo=emp rows
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}

### 17. EMPLOYEE reads own task → 200
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}

### 18. PM deletes a DONE task → 400 (only TODO is deletable)
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{pmToken}}
